quran[53]{c,v,t}:
  42,1,"Haa, Miim"
  42,2,"Ain, Siin, Qaaf"
  42,3,"Ko wano nii woni ko Allah Te…ó…óu…óo, √Ďee√Īo On wahayiniri e maa, e …ďen adinoo…ďe ma"
  42,4,"Ko Kanko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ko Kanko kadi woni Toowu…óo, Maw…óo On"
  42,5,"Kammuuli …óin no e…ď…ďa seekorgol dow majji, hara Malaa'ika'en no subbunhinanora yettugol Joomi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe insinanoo won…ďe ka leydi …ďen. Anndee pellet, ko Allah woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  42,6,"∆Āen non jogitii…ďe yi…ó…ďe goo gaanin Makko, Allah ko reenu…óo …ďe. A wonaali reenoowo …ďe"
  42,7,"Ko wano non Men wahayniri e maa…óa, janngeteende e aarabu, fii yo a jertin yim…ďe neene ca'e …óen e won…ďe takko mayre …ďen, jertinaa fii √Īalnde dental nden, - nde sikke alaa e mu'un - Fedde goo ka Aljnna, fedde goo kadi ka Yiite"
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O wa…óayno …ďe mofte goote. Kono himo On mo O muuyi ka Yurmeende Makko. Too√Īoo…ďe …ďen non, gi…óo alanaa …ďe, wanaa ballo"
  42,9,"Kaa …ďe jogiti yi…ó…ďe goo gaanin Makko? Awa ko Allah woni Gi…óo On, ko Kanko wuurnitata maay…ďe …ďen; ko Kanko kadi woni ka…ótan…óo kala huunde"
  42,10,"Kala ko luutondir…óon e fii mun, haray √Īaawoore mun nden ko ka Allah woni. Ko On moo…óon Allah, woni Joomi am; ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko kadi mi ruttorta [tuubugol]"
  42,11,"Fu…ó…óu…óo kamuuli …óin e leydi ndin. O wa…óiranii on e pittaali mon …óin genndoo…ďe, ka neemoraa…ói kadi nooneeji; Himo …óu…ó…óinira on …óum. Hay huunde yerondiraa e Makko; ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, Yi'oowo On"
  42,12,"Ko Kanko heerori soktir…óe kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo wertana arsike on mo O muuyani, O …ďi…ótinana (mo O muuyani). Pellet, ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde"
  42,13,"O sar'inanii on e diina kan, konko ko O yamirnoo Nuuhu, e kon ko Men wahayini e maa…óa, e kon ko Men yamirnoo Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa, wonnde: \"√Ďi…ďnee diina kan; hara on seertaali e makka\". Kono Ko noddotaa sirkoo…ďe …ďen e mun kon, mawnii e dow ma…ď…ďe. Allah non hino su…ďanoo …óum, mo O muuyani, O fewna e Makko, kala tuuboowo"
  42,14,"∆Āe seertaano, si wanaa …ďaawo nde ganndal ngal arde e ma…ď…ďe, sabu bewre hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Si wanaano fii Konngol ardinoongol, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e lajal ta∆īaangal, √Īaaweteno hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Ko pellet, roninaaa…ďe Deftere nden …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, hino e sikke fii mayre sikkitii…ďe"
  42,15,"Noddu (yim…ďe …ďen) kisan; √Īii…ďiraa no yamira…óaa non, wata a jokku mbelee…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, maakaa: \"Mi gom…óinii ko Allah jippini kon (fow) e Defte, mi yamiraama kadi, nun…óugol hakkunde mon. Allah woni Joomi amen e Joomi mon. Ko menen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Yeddondiral woo alaa hakkunde amen e mon. Allah moo…ďoyay e denndaandal. Ko ka Makko woni ruttorde nden"
  42,16,"∆Āen wennjiroo…ďe e diina Allah kan, …ďaawo ka ja…ďaneede, hujja ma…ď…ďe on ko meere, tikkere no fawii e ma…ď…ďe, hino woodani …ďe kadi lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippiniri Deftere nden goonga, e manndakke …óen. E ko anndin maa? Hino gasa hara Darngal ngal ko ko …ďadii"
  42,18,"∆Āeya …ďe gom…óinaali ngal …ďen, hi…ďe he√Īoringal; gom…óim…ďe …ďen kan, ko …ďe hulu fii maggal, e hoore hi…ďe felliti wonnde ko ngal goonga. Awa anndee won…ďe yeddondireede …ďen fii Darngal, ko pellet, …ďe wonii e nder majjere wo…ó…óunde"
  42,19,"Allah ko newanii…óo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Himo arsike on mo O muuyani. Ko Kanko woni Doolnu…óo, Foolu…óo On"
  42,20,"Kala taw…óo ko baraaje ndun laakara o faalaa, Men …ďeydanay mo mbarjaari makko ndin; kala kadi taw…óo ko jayru ndun aduna o yi…ói, Men okkay mo …óum, hara non o alaa ka kaalara (ton) ge…ďal"
  42,21,"Kaa hara denndaaaa…ói hino woodani …ďe, sar'inan…ói …ďe e diina kan, kon ko Allah duŇčaaki fii mun? Si wanaano fii Konngol [happunoongol] ngol fii senndugol [hakkunde ma…ď…ďe], √Īaaweteno hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Ko pellet, hino woodani too√Īu…ďe …ďen, lepte muusu…óe"
  42,22,"A yi'ay too√Īu…ďe …ďen hino huli e ko …ďe fggitii kon, …óum le ko yantay…óum e ma…ď…ďe. Gom…óim…ďe …ďen, …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe, hi…ďe e dinngire naakooji, hara hino woodani …ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, kala ko …ďe faaletee. Ko …óum tigiri, woni …ďural mawnungal ngal"
  42,23,"Ko …óum woni ko Allah wewlinirta jeyaa…ďe Makko gom…óim…ďe …ďen, …ďe golli golle mo∆ī∆īe. Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njo…ďdi e …óum, si wanaa tun giggol en…óam …óam\". Kala faggitii…óo mo∆ī∆īere, Men …ďeydanay mo mo∆ī∆īere e hoore mayre. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, mantoowo"
  42,24,"Kaa …ďe wi'ay o fefindor nde e hoore Allah fenaande. Si Allah haajuno, O notayno e …ďernda maa nden. Alla no meha meere nden, O tabintinira goonga kan Daalol Makko ngol. Pellet, ko O Anndu…óo gunndooji …ďer…óe …óen"
  42,25,"Ko Kanko woni ja…ďanoowo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen tuubuubuyee, O yaafoo bon…ói …óin, e hoore Himo anndi ko golloton kon"
  42,26,"Himo jaabinana gom…óim…ďe …ďen, …ďe golli mo∆ī∆īu…ói, O …ďeydana …ďe e …ďural Makko ngal. Heefer…ďe …ďen non, hino woodani …ďe lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah ya√Ī√Īanno jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen [fow] arsike, pellet, …ďe bewayno ka leydi; kono Himo jippinira emmbere ko O muuyi. Pellet, ko O Hummpitii…óo, yi*oowo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen"
  42,28,"Ko Kano woni jippinoowo to…ďo ngon …ďaawo …ďe ta∆īaade, O saaka yurmeende Makko nden. Ko Kanko kadi woni Gi…óo, Yettinii…óo On"
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e ruugay…ói …ói O saaki …óin hakkunde majji. Kanko e fii moo…ďindiroygol …ďe ngol, si O haajii, ko O hattan…óo"
  42,30,"Kala ko he…ďi on e masiibo, ko sabu ko juu…óe mon …óen faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non, ko …óuu…ói"
  42,31,"On wonaali laawotoo…ďe ka leydi ; alanaa on gaanin Allah, gi…óo, wanaa ballo"
  42,32,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko …óin: dogay…óe …óen ka maayo, wa'u…óe wa pelle"
  42,33,"Si O haajii, O dee∆īinay henndu ndun, ndu wa…ótinira tabitndu e hoore maggo. Wonii e …óum, maandeeji, wonannde kala mu√Ī√Īotoo…óo, yettoowo"
  42,34,Maa yoolira…óe sabu ko …ďe faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non ko …óuu…ói
  42,35,"Wennjoo…ďe …ďen e Aayeeje Amen …óen, hino anndi …ďe alaa laaworde"
  42,36,"Kala ko okka…óon e huunde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; ko ko woni ka Allah kon, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude woni kadi ko heddotoo wonannde gom…óim…ďe …ďen fawotoo…ďe e Joomi ma…ď…ďe"
  42,37,"wo…ó…óitotoo…ďe bakkaatuuji maw…ói …óin e pankare …óen, si wonii …ďe tikkii, hara …ďe yaafoto"
  42,38,"…ďen nootii…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe √Īi…ďni julde nden, …ďe tawata fiyaaku ma…ď…ďe on ko diisondiral hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, nafqoo…ďe e kon ko Men arsiki …ďe"
  42,39,"e …ďen taw…ďe si bewre he…ďii …ďe, …ďe yottoto"
  42,40,"Njo…ďdi bonnere, ko bone yeru mun. Kala non yaafii…óo o mo∆ī∆īintini, haray njo…ďdi makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yi…óaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďen"
  42,41,"Kala non yottii…ďe …ďaawo …ďe too√Īeede, ko …ďen woni …ďe laawol [nanngitireede] fawaaki e mun"
  42,42,"Ko laawol [nanngitireede] fawii e mun, ko too√Īoo…ďe yim…ďe …ďen, hara hi…ďe bewira e leydi ndin ko aldaa e goonga: …ďe …óon, hino woodani lepte muusu…óe"
  42,43,"Mu√Ī√Īii…óo on kadi o yaafii, ko pellet, …óum no jeyaa e pellital fiyakuujI"
  42,44,"Kala mo Allah majjini, haray gi…óo (goo) alanaa mo …ďaawo …óum. A tinay too√Īu…ďe …ďen, tuma …ďe yi'i lepte …óen, hi…ďe wi'a: \"Hara laawol ruttorde no woodi"
  42,45,"A tinay …ďe kadi, hi…ďe wee…ďitee e magge, hara hi…ďe yankinii koyeera on, hi…ďe ndaarira ndaar…óe leppagol. Gom…óim…ďe …ďen wi'aya: \"Ko woni hayru …ďe …ďen, ko …ďen hayrim…ďe ko'e mun e …ďeynguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óin √Ďalnde Darngal\". Anndee pellet, too√Īu…ďe …ďen no e lepte duumii…óe"
  42,46,"Yi…ó…ďe alanaa …ďe, ko wallitoo …ďe, hara wanaa Allah. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray laawol alanaa mo"
  42,47,"Nootee Joomi mon, ado √Īalaande arde, nde ruttoowo alaa …óum ka Allah. Nden √Īalnde, faaborde alanaa on, yeddugol kadi alanaa on"
  42,48,"Si …ďe …óuurnike non, haray Men nuliraali ma, aynoowo …ďe: fawaaki ma, si wanaa yottingol. Si wonii Men mee…óiniri ne…ó…óanke on neema immorde e Amen, o wewlira mo; si ko bone non he…ďi …ďe, sabu kon ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ardiniri, a taway pellet, ne…ó…óo on ko jeddu…óo sanne"
  42,49,"Ko Allah woodani laamagol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo taga ko O muuyi. Himo ye…óa mo O muuyani …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe, O ye…óa kadi mo O muuyani …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe"
  42,50,"maa O jillira …ďe wor…ďe e rew…ďe; Himo wa…óa dimaro, on mo O muuyani. Pellet, ko O Anndu…óo, Ha…ótan…óo"
  42,51,"Sellantaa ne…ó…óanke, nde Allah yewtata mo, si wanaa wahayu, maa e …ďaawo heedo, maa O immina Nulaa…óo (Malaa'ikaajo), on wayahina e duŇčayee(sakkitoore) Makko, kon ko O haaji. Pellet, ko O Toowu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
  42,52,"Ko wano non Men wayayinir e maa…óa, ruuhu on [Alqur'aana] e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni Deftere, maa gom…óinal; si ko woni, Men wa…óunde ndaygu, ngu Men fewnirta on mo Men muuyani e jeyaa…ďe Amen …ďen. Pellet, ko a fewnoowo e laawol focciingol"
  42,53,"laawol Allah, On jey…óo ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Anndee, ko ka Allah, fiyakuuji …óin ruttotoo"